     H            Y.
     F** UTLR02B *******************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: GET HOW MANY WORKING DAYS                *
     F*  FUNCTION: GET HOW MANY WORKING DAYS THERE ARE IN A GIVEN # OF DAYS
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA)  2024.11.25                     *
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR02B'
     F*                    PARM           $DT8    8
     F*                    PARM           $DAY1   4
     F*                    PARM           $DAY2   4
     F*  IN   $DT8  :  8A DATE FROM (YYYYMMDD)
     F*       $DAY1 :  4A DESIGNATED DAYS
     F*  OUT  $DAY2 :  4A WORKING DAYS
     F*
     F*  EX. HOW MANY WORKING DAYS($DAY2) FROM 20241224 ($DT8) IN 7 DAYS($DAY1)
     F*      ANS --> 3 DAYS ($DAY2)
     F*********************************************************************
     FAGDPL12 IF  E           K        DISK
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80K@DATE
     I                                        1   40K@DTYY
     I                                        5   60K@DTMM
     I                                        7   80K@DTDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80F8KA
     I                                        1   40F8KAYY
     I                                        5   60F8KAMM
     I                                        7   80F8KADD
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140SDATE
     I                                        1   60NOW
     I                                        7  140TODAY
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      *                    MAIN PROCESS
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     C                     EXSR #INIT
      * CHECK DATE
     C           K@PL12    SETLLAGDPL12
     C           1         DO   @DAY1
     C                     READ AGDPL12                  98
     C   98                LEAVE
      *
     C           F8HIRU    IFEQ '*'
     C           F8YORU    OREQ '*'
     C                     ITER
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ADD  1         @DAY2
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     MOVEL@DAY2     $DAY2
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
      *=============================================================
      *                    INITIAL PROCESS
      *=============================================================
     C           #INIT     BEGSR
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $DT8    8        IN
     C                     PARM           $DAY1   4        "
     C                     PARM           $DAY2   4        OUT
      *
     C           K@PL12    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@DTYY
     C                     KFLD           K@DTMM
     C                     KFLD           K@DTDD
      *
     C                     TIME           SDATE
     C                     MOVEL$DAY1     @DAY1   40
     C                     MOVEL'0000'    $DAY2
     C                     Z-ADD0         @DAY2   40
      *
     C           $DT8      IFEQ *BLANK
     C           $DT8      OREQ '00000000'
     C                     MOVELTODAY     $DT8
     C                     ENDIF
      * SET KEY
     C                     MOVEL$DT8      K@DATE
      *
     C                     ENDSR
